  &lt;li&gt;Graphical programming with &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ktalke12/Labview-MiP&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;LabVIEW&lt;/a&gt;, Cloud9 IDE on Node.js&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;plus much more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

